sequenceDiagram
    participant Tool as LangChain Tool
    participant Adapter as protect wrapper
    participant Interceptor as ToolInterceptor
    participant Resolver as SPIFFEResolver
    participant Eval as OPAEvaluator

    Tool->>Adapter: _run/_arun(...)
    Adapter->>Interceptor: intercept_or_raise(tool_name, tool_params)
    Interceptor->>Resolver: resolve() when identity missing
    Interceptor->>Interceptor: build ToolCallEvent
    Interceptor->>Eval: evaluate(event)
    Eval-->>Interceptor: PolicyDecision
    alt blocked/escalated
        Interceptor-->>Adapter: raise NorviqBlockError/NorviqEscalateError
    else allowed/audit
        Adapter-->>Tool: call original method
    end
